Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.40,0:00:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier 而那也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.63,0:00:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.87,0:00:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同時站在火線的兩端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.48,0:00:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞過危險的轉角追過生與死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.05,0:00:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑戰謊言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.89,0:00:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論編織出多少謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.53,0:00:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相還是會照出光明的輪廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.57,0:00:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.10,0:00:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.74,0:00:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我們的痛苦都拋在腦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.04,0:00:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.64,0:00:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.21,0:01:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是士兵不是站著就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.65,0:01:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.22,0:01:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佔好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.85,0:01:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它們留給審判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.12,0:01:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.69,0:01:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.46,0:01:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犧牲的時候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.16,0:01:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只能奮起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.43,0:01:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻殼機動隊 S.A.C. 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.52,0:01:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回家路上繞過去買
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.43,0:01:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太感謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.73,0:01:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道尺寸嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.36,0:01:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——直接穿脫型的L SIZE 對吧 ——那是爸爸對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.93,0:01:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——恩 ——媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.10,0:01:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.41,0:02:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.94,0:02:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要逃離開我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.85,0:02:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼眼神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.18,0:02:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.06,0:02:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把槍丟掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.76,0:02:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把痛覺切斷了 沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.53,0:03:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.26,0:03:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傷得怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.82,0:03:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.58,0:03:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼想找死嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.29,0:03:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#10 瘋狂的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.46,0:04:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總共打了12發子彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.66,0:04:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個數字沒錯吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.10,0:04:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.30,0:04:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來還得再拘留一陣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.27,0:04:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是為什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.08,0:04:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是公安9課的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.98,0:04:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.35,0:04:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是有可能要進行簡式審判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.72,0:04:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.09,0:04:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是受你父母委託替你辯護的律師上田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.26,0:04:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.50,0:04:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能不能想辦法盡快幫我換新的義體啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.83,0:04:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明沒有痛覺卻痛得受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.47,0:04:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.71,0:04:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩天內就可以出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.31,0:04:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 挨了那麼多顆子彈一定很痛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.71,0:04:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實那不過是件意外對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.78,0:04:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個義體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.15,0:04:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你改造過不少次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.02,0:05:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不但把不同廠商的零件裝在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.56,0:05:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每次也都改寫控制軟體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.83,0:05:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底想說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.20,0:05:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是專門打義體相關案件的律師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.40,0:05:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此對這類事情非常熟悉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.77,0:05:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算在一般情形下也有可能因為某種狀況造成控制機能失常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.61,0:05:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起訴狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.95,0:05:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因左列案件提起公訴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.08,0:05:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2032年9月9日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.92,0:05:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新濱地方檢察署檢察官森和臣檢事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.29,0:05:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新濱地方法院庭上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.53,0:05:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本籍 新濱縣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.50,0:05:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住所 新濱市住吉台2-B-5
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.93,0:05:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無職業的和泉勝彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.10,0:05:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2009年6月18日生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.37,0:05:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起訴事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.27,0:05:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被告對曾經交往過的新濱市市立醫院護士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.18,0:05:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靜野由加裏 當時24歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.48,0:06:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,數次要求復合卻遭拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.02,0:06:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我無法理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.02,0:06:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公 你又不是犯人卻遭到拘留
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.46,0:06:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也這麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.96,0:06:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 這是為了讓審判能盡快結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.63,0:06:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且雖說是為了救人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.86,0:06:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我確實在執勤時間外開了槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.40,0:06:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是非帶槍不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.77,0:06:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以辭去現在保全公司的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.80,0:06:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辭掉工作那我們一家四口吃什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.77,0:06:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.29,0:06:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,課長 抱歉讓您專程過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.53,0:06:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情過去了就不要再提
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.49,0:06:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的行動也有值得稱讚的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.20,0:06:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 問題在於你在下班時間開槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.47,0:06:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.10,0:06:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.74,0:06:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嫌犯的老爸是大公司的社長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.74,0:07:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至於擔任辯護人的那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.44,0:07:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是個在義體相關爭訟土不擇手段撈錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.84,0:07:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惡名昭彰的檢察官轉任律師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.31,0:07:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要小心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.38,0:07:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.48,0:07:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會做好心理準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.62,0:07:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隔離時的會面很可能成為反對詰問的材料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.72,0:07:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後就交給你自己判斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.36,0:07:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.43,0:07:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,此外 關於我內人的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.43,0:07:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個你放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.00,0:07:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經跟她說旁聽也會留下不好的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.37,0:07:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是回去比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.64,0:07:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太感謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.97,0:07:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後提醒你一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.27,0:07:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你應該已經知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.21,0:07:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,法庭內禁止任何通訊行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.08,0:07:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通常波段的通訊還會被反追蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.22,0:07:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時間差不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.12,0:07:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去做答辯的準備吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托古薩先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,調查報告上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.33,0:07:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,記載你集中射擊和泉先生的肩膀及雙腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.40,0:08:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目的是想阻止他的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.47,0:08:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上面是這麼記載的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.37,0:08:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼有必要開這麼多槍呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.97,0:08:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嫌犯有做義體化又說切斷了感覺器官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.11,0:08:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此我覺得有必要讓他完全無法行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.88,0:08:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,記得你說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.92,0:08:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你剛開始有出聲制止嫌犯的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.79,0:08:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.52,0:08:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是犯人並沒有放下槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.32,0:08:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從犯人手中取走兇器是遂行逮捕時的鐵則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.50,0:08:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.93,0:08:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 讓我們稍微改變一下看事情的角度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.60,0:08:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托古薩先生 你看過這個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.47,0:08:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.41,0:08:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那跟我執勤時用的槍同一型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.28,0:08:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.45,0:08:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是MATEBA公司制自動左輪槍的復製品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.05,0:08:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你工作的地方全員都使用這把槍嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.65,0:08:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.72,0:08:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他人使用SEBURO M5
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.49,0:08:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,SEBURO M5是一種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.09,0:09:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最多可連射21發5.7mm子彈的自動武器吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.63,0:09:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你的槍卻只有六發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.87,0:09:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不覺得這實在太沒效率了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.41,0:09:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托古薩先生 用這把槍的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.71,0:09:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,子彈打完了該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.48,0:09:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拋棄彈殼 裝填新的子彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.41,0:09:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我對槍不熟悉所以想請您說明一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.62,0:09:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左輪和自動武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.59,0:09:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪一種比較能夠快速更換子彈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.89,0:09:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然不能一概而論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.39,0:09:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想大致上是自動武器比較快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.10,0:09:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 左輪也有優點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.07,0:09:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托古薩先生 不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.70,0:09:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只要針對問題回答就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.10,0:09:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 我這樣問你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.54,0:09:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,SEBURO和MATEBA
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.97,0:09:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪一種裝填子彈比較快?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.28,0:09:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是SEBURO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.71,0:09:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.38,0:09:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在執行任務的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.78,0:09:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,故意選擇沒效率的槍來使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.09,0:10:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從你工作的性質來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.06,0:10:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是一件非常不自然的事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.19,0:10:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實有你說的這一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.10,0:10:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 左輪和自動武器不同 不會出現卡彈的情形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.33,0:10:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要不遇到太緊急的狀況這樣的裝彈數也足夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.24,0:10:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個理由沒什麼說服力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.97,0:10:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你現在就遇到這種狀況了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.44,0:10:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,講直接一點
