Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.45,0:10:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,YES還是N0？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.12,0:10:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這並不是因為喜好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.32,0:10:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 我再請教一個問題
