Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.27,0:10:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是不是原本就把射擊這個行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.20,0:10:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當作興趣嗜好來看呢?
