Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.92,0:11:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望辯方律師提出與本案直接相關的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.32,0:11:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.93,0:11:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 托古薩先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.63,0:11:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟您確認一下
