Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.11,0:11:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你對和泉先生大吼「那麼想找死嗎?」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.38,0:11:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的行動選項當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.18,0:11:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包括了殺死嫌疑犯的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.42,0:11:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.79,0:11:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.32,0:11:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這根本就只是抓人語病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.83,0:11:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,證人 請你坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.46,0:11:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事實上和泉先生的身體四肢關節都被子彈擊中...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.36,0:11:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你給我適可而止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.20,0:11:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的確開槍打了嫌犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.33,0:11:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過那是為了救女性被害人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.24,0:12:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看樣子你完全沒有反省
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.47,0:12:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要轉移焦點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.14,0:12:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問題是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.18,0:12:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,證人請你坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.68,0:12:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是審判長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.41,0:12:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.53,0:12:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣?還順利嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.09,0:12:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他相當憤慨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.70,0:12:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個律師意料之外的精明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.73,0:12:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是托古薩又不是被告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.24,0:12:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休庭前幾乎就像是被告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.08,0:12:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,密碼通訊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.58,0:12:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.91,0:12:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他切換成自閉模式了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.88,0:12:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他沒瞭解到我們跟他會面的意圖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.42,0:12:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托古薩雖然菜 但並不笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.99,0:12:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他早就察覺到我們打算做密碼通訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.96,0:12:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這表示他不想在法庭內使用卑鄙手段嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.73,0:12:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.90,0:13:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中途開始就完全不看我們這邊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.80,0:13:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去查查被告的底細
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.20,0:13:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校 你繼續旁聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.41,0:13:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也暫時先回本部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.81,0:13:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.54,0:13:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為托古薩先生有殺人的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.58,0:13:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.75,0:13:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在調查報告裏托古薩先生這樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.42,0:13:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「跟嫌犯對峙的時候」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.15,0:13:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「我一眼就判斷出這名男子全身都做過義體化」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.63,0:13:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托古薩先生的這段話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.39,0:13:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,違反義體安裝者歧視禁止法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.90,0:13:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.07,0:13:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本案近乎固執的開槍方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.47,0:13:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也可以認為是來自他對義體安裝者的歧視意識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.61,0:13:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,異議
