Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.55,0:13:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望辯方律師根據具體事實提出反論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.69,0:13:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.19,0:13:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.79,0:13:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想先談托古薩先生特殊的工作環境之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.46,0:14:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再進一步說明他的具體行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.83,0:14:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托古薩執勤的公安9課
