Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.39,0:14:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果這次事件就成為他內心黑暗面的發洩口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.92,0:14:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,異議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.12,0:14:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛的發言也是辯方律師無根據的臆測之詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.50,0:14:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,異議有效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.67,0:14:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,課長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.14,0:14:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在被告的終端機發現有趣的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.54,0:14:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犯罪前一天動手術安裝非法義體的存證信函
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.14,0:14:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用那個能擊敗他們嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.48,0:14:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姑且也算是證據吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.72,0:15:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將巴特找到的情報轉給檢方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.92,0:15:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.86,0:15:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 楠檢事想把9課拉上法庭的這條情報呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.40,0:15:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然上次逮捕藥島幹事長時這個男人就有動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.27,0:15:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 本案看來背後有人操縱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.80,0:15:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼說?
