Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.45,0:15:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是合田吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.21,0:15:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還真敢下手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.19,0:15:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.06,0:15:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸什麼時候回來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.43,0:15:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 什麼時候回來呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.86,0:15:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有何貴幹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.57,0:15:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在考慮對你提出民事訴訟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你打算威脅我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.61,0:15:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛我跟你的上司荒卷課長取得聯繫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.11,0:15:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他真是個通情達理的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.91,0:16:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了交換我撤回對你的民事訴訟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.32,0:16:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎同意把事情歸結到義體控制上的意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.65,0:16:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,課長不可能接受這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.02,0:16:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 請原諒我只能按照預定計劃進行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.86,0:16:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣一來 9課的人大概會很傷腦筋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.30,0:16:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管事情怎麼發展我都沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.07,0:16:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托古薩先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.48,0:16:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犯人如果是肉身的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.18,0:16:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也會開那麼多槍嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.25,0:16:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我當然會採取不同的應對方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.68,0:16:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
