Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.12,0:16:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想請教你隸屬的公安9課所採取的具體應對方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.36,0:16:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近頻頻發生義體化難民所犯下的自殺炸彈攻擊對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.03,0:16:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於這些事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.77,0:16:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽說公安9課密切參與調查行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.84,0:16:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問是真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.24,0:17:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.51,0:17:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就連數天前的連續自殺炸彈攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.51,0:17:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也親自去逮捕犯人這是事實嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.15,0:17:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.89,0:17:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對媒體進行情報管制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.79,0:17:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經在做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.62,0:17:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於那個事件這裏有一份提交給檢察官的報告書副本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.63,0:17:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根據這份報告書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.40,0:17:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托古薩先生在阻止義體化難民自爆的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.74,0:17:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然發出警告卻沒有開槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.41,0:17:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼對本案嫌犯和對那個意圖自爆的少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.75,0:17:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應對方式有這麼大的差異?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.78,0:17:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這很明顯是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.22,0:17:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你心裏有歧視意識的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.29,0:17:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.19,0:17:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這次事件當中我一開始也對嫌犯發出警告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.63,0:17:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是他所採取的行動完全不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.30,0:18:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想幫助向我求救的被害人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.43,0:18:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.24,0:18:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你沒有辦法證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.24,0:18:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們並不打算用這件事來審判你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.24,0:18:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只是想證明本案是因為你的行為引發的意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.22,0:18:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事實上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.05,0:18:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和泉先生在連續自殺攻擊案件發生後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.52,0:18:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,越來越常因為自身的義體化受到沒有道理的誤解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.39,0:18:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此為了讓大家能夠區別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.83,0:18:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,案發前一天才剛去換成一眼就知道不是難民的義手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.67,0:18:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還可以這樣掰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.27,0:18:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問話完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.11,0:18:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暫時休庭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.12,0:18:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.09,0:18:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種陰謀詭詐的審判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.89,0:18:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過世的被害人無法瞑目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.19,0:19:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天辯方律師跟我會面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.76,0:19:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用民事訴訟威脅我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.43,0:19:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逼我作證讓審判以意外結案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.93,0:19:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把我工作的地方執行特殊任務這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.94,0:19:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當作反對詰問的對象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.50,0:19:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是想逼我退縮的把戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.51,0:19:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 這種威脅已經沒用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.94,0:19:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.98,0:19:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我將在此辭去9課的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.62,0:19:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.42,0:19:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然被一時的激情所驅使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.36,0:19:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個事件不是意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.89,0:19:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 我無法救回被害人也是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.16,0:19:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想對我提出民事訴訟就儘管來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.30,0:19:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過相對的我絕對不會逃避這個審判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.21,0:19:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,證人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.34,0:19:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在休庭中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.08,0:19:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,證詞請在開庭之後提出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.68,0:19:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.91,0:19:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想把這些話說在前頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.05,0:19:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近跟義體普及率成正比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.82,0:20:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一類的審判也不斷增加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.29,0:20:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 聽說在這當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.45,0:20:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,某個特定義體製造商為了隱瞞自己公司商品的缺陷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.89,0:20:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與檢察官和律師勾結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.89,0:20:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進行不公正的審判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.66,0:20:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我因為工作性質自然對這類內幕十分熟悉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.40,0:20:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在既然決心辭去9課的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.57,0:20:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就打算說出一切真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.34,0:20:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你們也要有所覺悟喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.91,0:20:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶證人離開法庭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.70,0:20:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.90,0:20:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回來的真慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.97,0:20:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一點也不高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.54,0:20:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是少校也不該擅自製作靈魂侵入鑰匙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.51,0:20:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不服氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.18,0:21:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是因為你在那邊毫無意義地主張幼稚的正義感啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.48,0:21:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 那豈不是反效果嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.25,0:21:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.58,0:21:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後來嫌犯已經暫時被判有罪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.55,0:21:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正式審判也會確定有罪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.49,0:21:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校在那邊讓你說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.76,0:21:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是清查嫌犯辯護律師的帳戶後所得到的內幕情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.60,0:21:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他應該很怕自己的秘密曝光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.77,0:21:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.01,0:21:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用這次事件企圖打擊9課的楠檢事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.81,0:21:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該也會在自己與律師的關係曝光之前收手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.55,0:21:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,楠檢事是指那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.75,0:21:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.75,0:21:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次劇本恐怕是內廳的合田寫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.89,0:21:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,副導演是楠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.26,0:21:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主角則是那個檢察官轉任的律師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.49,0:21:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.63,0:21:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼我在法庭上爭取正義還有什麼意義?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.16,0:21:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.33,0:21:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的正義恐怕已經沒有出場的機會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.77,0:21:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣一來被害人無法瞑目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.04,0:22:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 也許會有天譴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.14,0:22:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天譴?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.02,0:22:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.02,0:22:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根據剛剛得到的新聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.05,0:22:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為扯上義體安裝者歧視禁止法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.02,0:22:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使得審判方向引發大眾注意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.99,0:22:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,護士命案的辯護律師和被告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.73,0:22:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——把這台車廢棄掉 ——在審判回家途中發生交通意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.30,0:22:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——書面資料也全部銷毀掉喔 ——律師重傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.03,0:22:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被告的義體似乎嚴重受損
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.80,0:22:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩人乘坐的車子在高速公路上行駛時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.87,0:22:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撞到中央分隔島導致翻車嚴重損壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.11,0:22:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上田律師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.32,0:22:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新濱地方明日放晴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.52,0:22:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該會是萬里晴空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.42,0:22:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.53,0:22:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——爸爸今天會回來嗎? ——預計最高溫29度 濕度70％
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.49,0:22:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——很快就會到家了 ——今晚應該是個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.76,0:22:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有如熱帶的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.98,0:23:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找出我體內行星和星星的銀河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.68,0:23:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著它們每一個都唱著同樣寧靜的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.26,0:23:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在現實當中從來沒看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.23,0:23:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的美麗事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.53,0:23:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有一點懷疑或恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.07,0:23:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽到一個聲音--醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.17,0:23:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到一個聲音呼喚我的名字--然後現出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.64,0:23:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我省視自身--醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.75,0:23:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到一道光隨時都圍繞著我--時間已經到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.05,0:23:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有真相 所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.45,0:23:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去讓這一切成真的--它就在裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.49,0:24:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在軀殼裏的美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.79,0:24:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽到一個聲音--醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.73,0:24:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到一個聲音呼喚我的名字--然後現出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.10,0:24:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我省視自身--醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.51,0:24:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到一道光隨時都圍繞著我--時間已經到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.74,0:24:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有真相 所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.01,0:24:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去讓這一切成真的--它就在裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.08,0:24:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在這個軀殼裏

